pl.sii.nnv.graph

Class Model

  • java.lang.Object
    • pl.sii.nnv.graph.Model

  • public class Model
extends java.lang.Object
    Model is class, which instance stores lists of all added cells (nodes) and edges (connectors). It is a part of graph class.
